J . B . Hunt to buy back up to 2 mln shrs . J . B . Hunt Transport Services Inc said on Thursday its board of directors had decided to buy back up to two million shares of common stock . The company said in a statement , " . . . the board also recognizes that an efficient use of its capital may be the repurchase of its common stock at prices that are attractive given the long - term outlook of the company . " Consequently , the board of directors has authorized the repurchase of up to two million shares of common stock . " The company has about 38 . 1 million shares outstanding . - - New York newsdesk , ( 212 ) 859 - 1610 
